=Episode 12=

28
00:01:44,950 --> 00:01:45,790
My Lady.

29
00:01:47,230 --> 00:01:48,070
My Lady.

30
00:02:07,350 --> 00:02:08,190
Where is His Highness?

31
00:02:08,840 --> 00:02:10,430
He left for court at Yin hour.

32
00:02:15,000 --> 00:02:16,430
Next time he goes to court,

33
00:02:16,630 --> 00:02:18,280
