to help him change.

34
00:02:18,710 --> 00:02:20,000
I need to act like
what I supposed to be.

35
00:02:20,910 --> 00:02:22,400
He grants me freedom
within the residence,

36
00:02:22,750 --> 00:02:24,430
so I must fulfill my duty as a consort.

37
00:02:24,750 --> 00:02:26,680
This is a win-win thing.

38
00:02:28,240 --> 00:02:30,840
Have you fulfilled your marriage
last night?

39
00:02:31,280 --> 00:02:32,520
There's no need for that.

40
00:02:33,150 --> 00:02:34,710
As long as he plays his role well,

41
00:02:34,710 --> 00:02:35,550
that's enough.

42
00:02:36,960 --> 00:02:38,240
Are you really not planning

43
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:40,280
to fulfill it with His Highness?

44
00:02:45,430 --> 00:02:46,630
After all that has happened,

45
00:02:47,310 --> 00:02:48,710
romance is hardly worth mentioning.

46
00:03:04,710 --> 00:03:06,400
What a coincidence, Mr. Wensheng.

47
00:03:06,630 --> 00:03:07,520
No wonder these days

48
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:08,870
you've been nowhere to be found.

49
00:03:08,870 --> 00:03:11,120
So you were hiding here
at Songling Academy.

50
00:03:17,910 --> 00:03:18,840
It hurts, it hurts!

51
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,960
Mr. Lu, that's not correct.

52
00:03:24,470 --> 00:03:26,870
I have been studying here all along.

53
00:03:27,400 --> 00:03:28,590
But seeing you here,

54
00:03:29,190 --> 00:03:31,310
it seems your esteemed father
has made quite an effort.

55
00:03:31,310 --> 00:03:32,150
It hurts!

56
00:03:38,840 --> 00:03:39,680
Lu Chang,

57
00:03:40,240 --> 00:03:41,750
you infiltrated my Lu family,

58
00:03:41,840 --> 00:03:43,710
cutting off my path to patronage. Why?

59
00:03:43,800 --> 00:03:44,870
Come, let's go see the magistrate.

60
00:03:48,080 --> 00:03:48,920
OK then.

61
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:51,120
With my status
as a Prefectural Graduate,

62
00:03:51,840 --> 00:03:54,710
I'll surely cause a huge stir in court.

63
00:03:55,080 --> 00:03:56,750
By then, all the filthy deeds
you've done

64
00:03:56,750 --> 00:03:58,190
will spread across every street
and alley.

65
00:03:58,630 --> 00:04:00,560
Even Songling Academy won't be able
to keep you.

66
00:04:00,960 --> 00:04:02,910
Have you thought about how to explain it
to your father?

67
00:04:05,560 --> 00:04:06,750
You're truly cunning!

68
00:04:07,470 --> 00:04:08,310
Mr. Lu,

69
00:04:08,750 --> 00:04:09,960
I advise you not to waste

70
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,400
your father's good intentions.

71
00:04:11,750 --> 00:04:14,400
Behave yourself and focus on
your studies.

72
00:04:14,750 --> 00:04:15,590
Also,

73
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,390
the next time you see me,

74
00:04:17,870 --> 00:04:19,600
if you dare to be so rude again,

75
00:04:20,120 --> 00:04:20,960
I won't mind

76
00:04:20,980 --> 00:04:22,510
teaching you a proper lesson.

77
00:04:27,560 --> 00:04:28,400
Lu Chang,

78
00:04:28,830 --> 00:04:29,920
just you wait!

79
00:04:33,270 --> 00:04:34,110
Get lost!

80
00:04:39,310 --> 00:04:40,750
I humbly congratulate you

81
00:04:40,750 --> 00:04:43,480
on your wedding, My Lady.

82
00:04:43,830 --> 00:04:45,800
I wish My Lady and His Highness

83
00:04:46,750 --> 00:04:50,240
a hundred years of harmony
and early offspring.

84
00:04:50,430 --> 00:04:51,870
What is this, Lu Mingshu?

85
00:04:52,160 --> 00:04:53,160
If you keep talking like that,

86
00:04:53,160 --> 00:04:54,120
I'll back out!

87
00:04:54,920 --> 00:04:55,760
You mustn't!

88
00:04:56,870 --> 00:04:57,920
Dear sister,

89
00:04:57,920 --> 00:04:58,760
dear Shujun,

90
00:04:58,920 --> 00:05:00,070
I have something good for you.

91
00:05:00,560 --> 00:05:01,400
What is it?

92
00:05:02,510 --> 00:05:04,120
These are the pair bracelets I designed.

93
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:05,750
It's my wedding gift to you.

94
00:05:06,040 --> 00:05:06,880
Take a look.

95
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,190
It's just a political marriage,

96
00:05:08,510 --> 00:05:10,190
yet you put so much thought
into blessing me.

97
00:05:12,560 --> 00:05:13,920
But these bracelets are truly beautiful.

98
00:05:14,720 --> 00:05:16,920
Mingshu, you're amazing!

99
00:05:17,920 --> 00:05:19,000
It's not bad,

100
00:05:26,240 --> 00:05:29,360
but at most, it's just some
clever handiwork.

101
00:05:29,360 --> 00:05:31,480
(County Princess Wen'an)
But I don't see the decisiveness,

102
00:05:31,630 --> 00:05:32,800
wit, and chivalrous spirit

103
00:05:32,800 --> 00:05:34,160
you mentioned.

104
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:36,880
Is this young lady

105
00:05:37,120 --> 00:05:39,000
really as impressive as you say?

106
00:05:40,720 --> 00:05:42,310
And this lady is?

107
00:05:43,310 --> 00:05:45,120
Mingshu, let me introduce you.

108
00:05:45,430 --> 00:05:47,070
This is my close friend,

109
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:49,160
the County Princess Wen'an.

110
00:05:49,160 --> 00:05:50,830
She's also a cousin of Mr. Song.

111
00:05:51,950 --> 00:05:54,000
Greetings, My Lady.

112
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,000
No need for formalities.

113
00:05:58,160 --> 00:05:59,920
Actually, she came here today

114
00:06:00,040 --> 00:06:01,680
to ask you for a favor.

115
00:06:13,240 --> 00:06:14,390
You handled the matter

116
00:06:14,920 --> 00:06:16,000
of the Yin family well.

117
00:06:16,430 --> 00:06:17,750
I admire your independent judgment,

118
00:06:18,070 --> 00:06:19,270
your refusal to blindly

119
00:06:19,560 --> 00:06:20,720
go with the flow.

120
00:06:22,510 --> 00:06:23,680
You flatter me.

121
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:25,600
If there's anything you need,

122
00:06:25,600 --> 00:06:26,510
please feel free to say it.

123
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:28,480
Please help me investigate someone.

124
00:06:29,120 --> 00:06:29,960
Investigate someone?

125
00:06:32,630 --> 00:06:33,600
Forgive my bluntness,

126
00:06:33,950 --> 00:06:35,920
but you, My Lady,
were raised in the capital,

127
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:36,950
with a noble family background.

128
00:06:37,510 --> 00:06:39,920
Whether in terms of connections
or means,

129
00:06:39,920 --> 00:06:41,000
you surpass me greatly.

130
00:06:41,430 --> 00:06:42,720
I've only just arrived in the capital,

131
00:06:42,720 --> 00:06:44,680
and matters like investigations...

132
00:06:44,680 --> 00:06:46,510
If I'm asking you to investigate,

133
00:06:46,510 --> 00:06:47,750
there's naturally a reason.

134
00:06:48,680 --> 00:06:50,510
You're asking for help,
yet you're yelling?

135
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:53,800
Mingshu, she's just impatient,

136
00:06:53,800 --> 00:06:54,800
don't mind her.

137
00:06:55,750 --> 00:06:57,040
What's truly bothering her

138
00:06:57,720 --> 00:06:59,120
is her engagement.

139
00:07:00,000 --> 00:07:02,830
She was betrothed three years ago
to Xie Xi,

140
00:07:03,120 --> 00:07:04,600
the eldest son of Marquis Yongqing.

141
00:07:04,950 --> 00:07:06,830
She's set to marry him next year.

142
00:07:07,310 --> 00:07:09,680
Xie Xi is said to be gentle, talented,

143
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,040
and possesses excellent character.

144
00:07:11,240 --> 00:07:12,750
He's considered an ideal husband.

145
00:07:13,160 --> 00:07:14,630
Doesn't sound like there's a problem.

146
00:07:14,630 --> 00:07:16,040
Everyone says there's no problem,

147
00:07:16,040 --> 00:07:17,390
but I just feel something's wrong.

148
00:07:17,920 --> 00:07:19,040
Why do you think so?

149
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:22,750
But Xie Xi has always obeyed
your every word.

150
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:24,430
You said he no longer
treats you as he did before,

151
00:07:24,580 --> 00:07:25,430
yet everyone told you

152
00:07:25,430 --> 00:07:26,360
to stop making trouble.

153
00:07:30,560 --> 00:07:32,000
Though I didn't fully understand,

154
00:07:32,000 --> 00:07:33,240
I was afraid of misunderstanding her,

155
00:07:33,630 --> 00:07:35,160
so I agreed to let her
investigate him in secret.

156
00:07:35,600 --> 00:07:37,430
But after following Xie Xi
for more than half a year,

157
00:07:37,430 --> 00:07:38,680
there's been no findings at all.

158
00:07:39,750 --> 00:07:40,750
Now even I'm starting to wonder

159
00:07:40,750 --> 00:07:42,000
if you're making a fuss over nothing.

160
00:07:42,680 --> 00:07:44,190
How could even you not believe me?

161
00:07:44,630 --> 00:07:46,000
It's not that I don't believe you.

162
00:07:46,430 --> 00:07:47,480
Then explain clearly:

163
00:07:47,480 --> 00:07:48,720
why do you suspect him?

164
00:07:49,430 --> 00:07:51,270
I can't say exactly why.

165
00:07:51,680 --> 00:07:53,270
It's just a feeling. Understand?

166
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:54,600
Calm down, My Lady.

167
00:07:55,160 --> 00:07:56,070
Think carefully:

168
00:07:56,240 --> 00:07:57,600
why would you have such a feeling?

169
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:02,160
Xie Xi has always

170
00:08:03,920 --> 00:08:05,480
been tolerant with me.

171
00:08:05,680 --> 00:08:06,920
Even when I throw tantrums,

172
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:07,760
he still

173
00:08:08,070 --> 00:08:09,040
treats me with patience.

174
00:08:09,240 --> 00:08:10,830
That's why my parents

175
00:08:10,830 --> 00:08:12,270
are pleased with this engagement.

176
00:08:12,510 --> 00:08:14,430
But, since last year,

177
00:08:14,870 --> 00:08:16,390
I always feel something's wrong.

178
00:08:17,040 --> 00:08:18,070
Even though

179
00:08:18,430 --> 00:08:20,630
he remains courteous and respectful,

180
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:23,190
sometimes, there's a thin line

181
00:08:24,920 --> 00:08:26,720
between politeness and distance.

182
00:08:29,120 --> 00:08:31,630
You suspect he has someone else
in his heart?

183
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,720
When choosing a husband, I do not seek

184
00:08:34,870 --> 00:08:36,120
high status or immense wealth,

185
00:08:36,120 --> 00:08:38,510
but I must have a man
of noble character,

186
00:08:38,510 --> 00:08:39,720
faithful and unwavering.

187
00:08:39,720 --> 00:08:40,960
Xie Xi knows well

188
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:42,000
what I expect of him.

189
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:43,870
But if he's had

190
00:08:45,080 --> 00:08:46,910
a change of heart

191
00:08:47,320 --> 00:08:48,720
and continues to deceive me,

192
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,870
then he must have another agenda.

193
00:08:50,320 --> 00:08:51,510
I would never marry

194
00:08:51,510 --> 00:08:53,440
a hypocritical villain
with ulterior motives.

195
00:08:55,270 --> 00:08:56,110
My Lady,

196
00:08:56,670 --> 00:08:57,910
I understand your concern.

197
00:08:58,240 --> 00:08:59,080
I'm willing to help you.

198
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:02,440
Really?

199
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,840
I have always despised

200
00:09:04,840 --> 00:09:05,680
those who are fickle

201
00:09:05,680 --> 00:09:06,840
and toy with sincere feelings.

202
00:09:07,240 --> 00:09:08,120
Besides, by doing this,

203
00:09:08,120 --> 00:09:09,840
you're taking responsibility
for your own happiness.

204
00:09:10,440 --> 00:09:12,510
It's better to find out before marriage

205
00:09:12,510 --> 00:09:14,270
than to regret it afterward,

206
00:09:14,270 --> 00:09:15,110
right?

207
00:09:15,870 --> 00:09:16,710
I support you.

208
00:09:17,150 --> 00:09:18,840
You are indeed, as Shujun said,

209
00:09:18,840 --> 00:09:20,720
a loyal and righteous friend
worth trusting.

210
00:09:22,150 --> 00:09:24,240
No matter what you find out,

211
00:09:24,630 --> 00:09:25,480
I'll be grateful to you.

212
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:28,270
My Lady, you are too kind.

213
00:09:30,390 --> 00:09:31,230
By the way,

214
00:09:31,320 --> 00:09:32,870
Xie Xi will attend
the Wine Tasting event

215
00:09:32,870 --> 00:09:34,320
before the Metropolitan Exam tomorrow.

216
00:09:34,670 --> 00:09:37,000
I'll arrange for you to meet him there.

217
00:09:37,550 --> 00:09:39,440
I was planning to attend
that event anyway.

218
00:09:40,510 --> 00:09:41,390
I'll do as you say.

219
00:09:42,720 --> 00:09:44,200
The Wine Tasting event will be bustling.

220
00:09:44,630 --> 00:09:45,840
All the young ladies of the capital

221
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,480
will go there to admire the gentlemen.

222
00:09:47,750 --> 00:09:49,080
If you're going,

223
00:09:49,510 --> 00:09:51,030
you must dress up nicely.

224
00:10:01,870 --> 00:10:03,910
You plan to use the Wine Tasting event

225
00:10:04,360 --> 00:10:05,360
to help Mr. Lu.

226
00:10:05,910 --> 00:10:07,120
Mr. Lu is full of talent.

227
00:10:07,910 --> 00:10:09,320
If he can showcase a little of it

228
00:10:09,320 --> 00:10:10,320
at the event,

229
00:10:10,720 --> 00:10:12,510
he will surely rise to fame
in the capital.

230
00:10:13,910 --> 00:10:15,440
And with so many noble ladies
gathering today,

231
00:10:16,000 --> 00:10:17,600
if I can help Mr. Lu find a good match,

232
00:10:18,030 --> 00:10:19,760
it will benefit my future interactions
with Mingshu.

233
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:22,030
Impressive.

234
00:10:25,150 --> 00:10:26,120
From what I see,

235
00:10:26,390 --> 00:10:28,270
she only has a budding affection
for Mr. Song.

236
00:10:28,360 --> 00:10:30,360
(Jinzun Restaurant)
She hasn't truly fallen for him yet.

237
00:10:31,440 --> 00:10:32,300
Please come in.

238
00:10:32,510 --> 00:10:33,350
Since you...

239
00:10:34,960 --> 00:10:37,200
You mustn't let her fall for
someone else.

240
00:10:37,440 --> 00:10:38,320
This way, miss.

241
00:10:38,320 --> 00:10:39,160
No matter what,

242
00:10:40,270 --> 00:10:41,630
as long as she feels happy and blessed,

243
00:10:42,170 --> 00:10:43,360
- that's enough.
- This way, ladies.

244
00:10:46,840 --> 00:10:47,680
That's all I have to say.

245
00:10:48,080 --> 00:10:49,440
I still have official duties
to attend to.

246
00:10:49,670 --> 00:10:50,510
From here on,

247
00:10:50,870 --> 00:10:51,720
it's up to you.

248
00:11:00,920 --> 00:11:01,760
This way, miss.

249
00:11:02,320 --> 00:11:03,820
(Jinzun Restaurant)
Mr. Lu,

250
00:11:03,840 --> 00:11:04,680
why don't you get inside?

251
00:11:05,550 --> 00:11:06,390
I'm waiting for Mingshu.

252
00:11:06,390 --> 00:11:07,240
I'll wait with you.

253
00:11:09,910 --> 00:11:10,750
Mr. Lu,

254
00:11:11,080 --> 00:11:12,490
I know you view the Wine Tasting event

255
00:11:12,500 --> 00:11:13,440
as a vanity fair,

256
00:11:13,750 --> 00:11:15,600
but its influence is far beyond
what you imagine.

257
00:11:15,600 --> 00:11:16,450
This way, sir.

258
00:11:16,460 --> 00:11:18,510
You can make a name for yourself
by winning,

259
00:11:18,910 --> 00:11:20,390
and be favored by the noble ladies, becoming

260
00:11:20,600 --> 00:11:21,600
an ideal husband candidate.

261
00:11:23,550 --> 00:11:24,550
In that case,

262
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:27,120
- you must give it your all
- Please come in, miss.

263
00:11:27,320 --> 00:11:28,360
and seize the top prize.

264
00:11:28,960 --> 00:11:30,550
I only wish to accompany my sister

265
00:11:30,550 --> 00:11:31,390
and experience the event.

266
00:11:31,550 --> 00:11:32,720
I can accompany her too.

267
00:11:33,510 --> 00:11:34,510
Today's opportunity is rare.

268
00:11:35,270 --> 00:11:36,670
You must make connections for

269
00:11:36,910 --> 00:11:37,750
your future prospects.

270
00:11:38,270 --> 00:11:39,270
Mr. Song, you really

271
00:11:39,750 --> 00:11:41,320
have put in so much effort for me.

272
00:11:43,240 --> 00:11:44,080
Brother.

273
00:11:44,910 --> 00:11:45,750
Qingzhao.

274
00:11:56,780 --> 00:12:00,100
(Jinzun Restaurant)

275
00:12:08,290 --> 00:12:11,420
♪Two swallows dart
through the drizzle♪

276
00:12:11,690 --> 00:12:14,670
♪A lonely shadow
