277
00:12:15,780 --> 00:12:18,430
♪Thoughts lie concealed♪

278
00:12:18,740 --> 00:12:22,270
♪With no one to talk to♪

279
00:12:23,150 --> 00:12:26,360
♪Things will be changed♪

280
00:12:26,660 --> 00:12:29,510
♪At least, I have your shoulders♪

281
00:12:29,510 --> 00:12:30,450
Chang.

282
00:12:30,470 --> 00:12:32,540
♪Always by my side♪

283
00:12:33,310 --> 00:12:36,590
♪Shining bright as fireflies♪

284
00:12:47,120 --> 00:12:49,630
Mingshu, you look stunning today.

285
00:12:50,630 --> 00:12:51,470
Thank you.

286
00:12:53,390 --> 00:12:54,790
Brother, what's wrong?

287
00:12:56,200 --> 00:12:57,320
Your outfit today

288
00:12:58,600 --> 00:12:59,790
suits you very well.

289
00:13:03,240 --> 00:13:05,600
You know how to say sweet words now.

290
00:13:05,830 --> 00:13:06,960
I'll take it as a compliment from you.

291
00:13:07,790 --> 00:13:09,270
You really should advise your brother.

292
00:13:09,720 --> 00:13:11,440
I urged him to make more acquaintances,

293
00:13:11,720 --> 00:13:13,120
but he remains unmoved, only thinking about

294
00:13:13,360 --> 00:13:14,320
taking care of you.

295
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:17,150
Brother, you should
tend to your own matters.

296
00:13:17,150 --> 00:13:18,510
I can follow Qingzhao.

297
00:13:19,440 --> 00:13:20,280
It's fine.

298
00:13:24,960 --> 00:13:25,800
Have you

299
00:13:27,150 --> 00:13:28,200
embroidered green bamboo

300
00:13:28,200 --> 00:13:29,510
on every outfit of your?

301
00:13:33,750 --> 00:13:34,590
Let's go in.

302
00:13:36,780 --> 00:13:38,300
(Jinzun Restaurant)

303
00:13:38,320 --> 00:13:40,510
The Wine Tasting event is a way
for the taverns

304
00:13:40,510 --> 00:13:41,480
to attract customers

305
00:13:41,790 --> 00:13:42,910
when opening new batches of wine.

306
00:13:44,150 --> 00:13:45,200
The attending scholars compete

307
00:13:45,200 --> 00:13:47,240
by composing poetry and couplets
to determine the winner.

308
00:13:48,000 --> 00:13:49,790
The winner gets to choose
a barrel of wine

309
00:13:49,790 --> 00:13:50,670
to inscribe a poem on.

310
00:13:51,030 --> 00:13:52,280
(Luming Banquet)
Afterwards, the others

311
00:13:52,290 --> 00:13:53,510
choose their wine and compose poems.

312
00:13:53,660 --> 00:13:54,550
(Junzitai)

313
00:13:54,550 --> 00:13:55,550
These wine barrels

314
00:13:55,550 --> 00:13:57,160
(Tianchun Wine)
must not be opened before the exams.

315
00:13:57,510 --> 00:13:59,080
After the exam, the wine
the top scorer chose

316
00:13:59,320 --> 00:14:01,000
will be celebrated as
the "Top Scholar's Wine,"

317
00:14:01,460 --> 00:14:02,550
(Dongting Spring)
and the tavern

318
00:14:02,550 --> 00:14:03,870
(Jingting Pavilion)
will also gain fame.

319
00:14:05,390 --> 00:14:07,790
Thus, the scholar most likely to win

320
00:14:07,790 --> 00:14:09,200
will be highly sought after
by the taverns.

321
00:14:09,910 --> 00:14:11,840
It's inevitable that people
pursue fame and profit.

322
00:14:12,720 --> 00:14:13,910
That's why I urged you

323
00:14:13,910 --> 00:14:15,960
not to miss the chance
to showcase your talents.

324
00:14:17,150 --> 00:14:19,390
My brother doesn't care
about empty fame.

325
00:14:20,200 --> 00:14:21,440
But sometimes,a bit of fame

326
00:14:21,750 --> 00:14:23,030
makes it easier to navigate the capital.

327
00:14:27,000 --> 00:14:27,840
That's Mr. Song.

328
00:14:28,320 --> 00:14:30,120
He'll definitely be the top scholar
this year.

329
00:14:30,910 --> 00:14:32,360
Such a handsome gentleman!

330
00:14:33,080 --> 00:14:33,920
Qingzhao,

331
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:35,600
everyone's looking at you.

332
00:14:38,360 --> 00:14:39,720
But the one I care about isn't them.

333
00:14:51,270 --> 00:14:52,240
I'll go take a look there.

334
00:14:56,400 --> 00:14:58,190
Sir, come try our wine!

335
00:14:58,190 --> 00:15:00,420
Miss, our new wine!

336
00:15:02,080 --> 00:15:03,120
Sir, sir,

337
00:15:03,550 --> 00:15:04,670
can you come try

338
00:15:04,670 --> 00:15:05,790
our wine?

339
00:15:06,540 --> 00:15:07,390
Where is it?

340
00:15:07,510 --> 00:15:08,350
Over there.

341
00:15:13,840 --> 00:15:14,680
Have a seat.

342
00:15:15,510 --> 00:15:16,720
Can I try your wine?

343
00:15:16,720 --> 00:15:17,600
Alright.

344
00:15:24,360 --> 00:15:25,200
Please.

345
00:15:25,750 --> 00:15:26,590
Thank you.

346
00:15:34,600 --> 00:15:35,670
The wine is thick,

347
00:15:36,360 --> 00:15:37,480
sweet and mellow.

348
00:15:38,510 --> 00:15:39,360
It's a fine wine.

349
00:15:40,360 --> 00:15:41,360
Does this wine have a name?

350
00:15:42,320 --> 00:15:43,600
Our humble shop is unknown,

351
00:15:43,960 --> 00:15:44,960
no one asks about it.

352
00:15:45,750 --> 00:15:48,150
This wine is brewed from pine pollen,

353
00:15:48,960 --> 00:15:49,910
and has no name.

354
00:15:54,150 --> 00:15:56,240
An unknown man drinking unknown wine,

355
00:15:57,200 --> 00:15:58,390
how fitting.

356
00:15:59,750 --> 00:16:02,630
You are no ordinary person.

357
00:16:09,150 --> 00:16:09,990
Sir.

358
00:16:10,510 --> 00:16:12,030
Sir, please try mine!

359
00:16:12,030 --> 00:16:12,870
Mr. Xie is here!

360
00:16:12,870 --> 00:16:13,960
- Mr. Xie!
- Mr. Xie!

361
00:16:14,390 --> 00:16:15,230
Mr. Xie!

362
00:16:17,120 --> 00:16:18,030
Gentlemen.

363
00:16:18,320 --> 00:16:19,510
And this is?

364
00:16:20,750 --> 00:16:22,750
He is Xie Xi,
the son of Marquis Yongqing,

365
00:16:23,200 --> 00:16:24,360
and a hot favorite to top

366
00:16:24,360 --> 00:16:25,480
this year's spring exam.

367
00:16:25,790 --> 00:16:26,630
However, he's already

368
00:16:26,750 --> 00:16:28,320
- engaged to County Princess.
- Not at all, not at all.

369
00:16:28,440 --> 00:16:30,360
(Xie Xi)
So he's already occupied.

370
00:16:30,550 --> 00:16:33,120
I heard Shujun mention this.

371
00:16:33,390 --> 00:16:34,390
In your opinion,

372
00:16:34,670 --> 00:16:36,030
is he worthy of the county princess?

373
00:16:38,360 --> 00:16:39,550
He's indeed a hot contender

374
00:16:39,550 --> 00:16:40,550
for the top scorer this year.

375
00:16:40,870 --> 00:16:42,200
He has great talent and character,

376
00:16:42,480 --> 00:16:44,120
and he's quite respected
among his peers.

377
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:46,240
Both the headmaster and the tutors value him.

378
00:16:46,550 --> 00:16:47,390
He is a fine match.

379
00:16:48,360 --> 00:16:49,200
Mr. Song is here.

380
00:16:49,480 --> 00:16:50,550
Mr. Song! Mr. Song!

381
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:52,360
- Please try our wine!
- No, no,

382
00:16:52,720 --> 00:16:53,960
thank you, thank you.

383
00:16:54,270 --> 00:16:55,320
It's rich in fragrance.

384
00:16:55,320 --> 00:16:56,240
Thank you, everyone.

385
00:16:56,360 --> 00:16:57,320
Where's Brother?

386
00:16:57,320 --> 00:16:58,320
Have a taste.

387
00:16:58,320 --> 00:16:59,360
Mr. Xie, Mr. Xie,

388
00:16:59,510 --> 00:17:00,480
try our wine!

389
00:17:00,480 --> 00:17:01,870
Ours is better!

390
00:17:02,850 --> 00:17:03,720
Mr. Xie,

391
00:17:03,720 --> 00:17:05,350
come try our Tianzhong Wine!

392
00:17:05,350 --> 00:17:07,350
This wine has excellent flavor.

393
00:17:07,350 --> 00:17:08,840
- Then I'll have a taste.
- Ours is good too!

394
00:17:09,160 --> 00:17:10,110
What about another drink?

395
00:17:10,110 --> 00:17:10,950
Brother!

396
00:17:13,310 --> 00:17:14,160
I thought you forgot me.

397
00:17:14,960 --> 00:17:17,160
Those people only know
to fawn over power,

398
00:17:17,160 --> 00:17:18,400
blind to true talent.

399
00:17:18,790 --> 00:17:19,720
I'm afraid you

400
00:17:20,200 --> 00:17:21,040
might feel hurt.

401
00:17:21,750 --> 00:17:23,960
I am drinking and chatting happily

402
00:17:24,110 --> 00:17:25,000
with the old gentlemen.

403
00:17:25,510 --> 00:17:26,880
No need to worry about that.

404
00:17:41,240 --> 00:17:42,080
It's starting, Brother!

405
00:17:44,240 --> 00:17:45,080
It is time.

406
00:17:45,350 --> 00:17:46,190
I hereby announce

407
00:17:46,440 --> 00:17:47,280
the start of the

408
00:17:47,640 --> 00:17:48,510
Wine Tasting event.

409
00:17:49,030 --> 00:17:49,880
Everyone,

410
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,750
this year's gathering is hosted
by my Jinzun Restaurant.

411
00:17:52,880 --> 00:17:54,720
It is my honor to have the privilege.

412
00:17:55,350 --> 00:17:57,160
Talented scholars

413
00:17:57,160 --> 00:17:58,270
from all over

414
00:17:58,510 --> 00:17:59,680
have answered the invitation,

415
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:02,310
bringing great honor
to Jinzun Restaurant.

416
00:18:02,590 --> 00:18:04,750
- Well said!
- Well said!

417
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:11,310
Everyone, please look,

418
00:18:11,550 --> 00:18:13,680
this golden goblet was crafted

419
00:18:13,790 --> 00:18:15,070
at great expense by us.

420
00:18:15,200 --> 00:18:17,350
Later, the winner of the poetry contest

421
00:18:17,550 --> 00:18:19,400
will take home the golden goblet.

422
00:18:19,400 --> 00:18:21,310
The design of the goblet
follows ancient styles,

423
00:18:21,480 --> 00:18:23,550
with patterns resembling
auspicious clouds.

424
00:18:24,480 --> 00:18:26,350
If I place it in Hualang Pavilion,

425
00:18:26,590 --> 00:18:28,070
it would certainly have special meaning.

426
00:18:30,480 --> 00:18:32,270
Then, following tradition,

427
00:18:32,510 --> 00:18:35,000
I, as the host, shall present
the first line.

428
00:18:35,000 --> 00:18:37,160
Scholars, listen carefully:

429
00:18:37,550 --> 00:18:38,790
Feasts start by will,

430
00:18:39,110 --> 00:18:40,880
yet end beyond will;

431
00:18:41,270 --> 00:18:42,480
Partings and meetings,

432
00:18:42,880 --> 00:18:44,070
best be lightly borne.

433
00:18:46,880 --> 00:18:49,920
What a line!

434
00:18:50,270 --> 00:18:51,110
Easy to say,

435
00:18:52,110 --> 00:18:52,950
hard to do.

436
00:18:56,270 --> 00:18:58,070
Fine wine stirs the soul,

437
00:18:58,550 --> 00:19:00,070
its fragrance stirs the soul;

438
00:19:00,790 --> 00:19:03,480
A lingering bouquet drifts from the cup.

439
00:19:06,680 --> 00:19:08,000
Mr. Xie is truly talented!

440
00:19:08,350 --> 00:19:09,960
Among all the talents in the world,

441
00:19:09,960 --> 00:19:12,030
Mr. Xie must possess
eight tenths of them.

442
00:19:12,590 --> 00:19:14,480
Mr. Xie, please give the next line.

443
00:19:15,350 --> 00:19:17,240
(Luming Banquet)
Fine wine may ease all grief;

444
00:19:17,400 --> 00:19:19,920
At such a feast,
none should bear sorrow.

445
00:19:20,440 --> 00:19:23,310
At such a feast,
none should bear sorrow...

446
00:19:24,850 --> 00:19:26,090
This is a really hard one.

447
00:19:35,400 --> 00:19:36,750
Fair halls resemble painted scenes;

448
00:19:37,680 --> 00:19:39,200
All who lean on the rail
seem part of the picture.

449
00:19:39,350 --> 00:19:41,510
- Excellent!
- Really excellent!

450
00:19:43,550 --> 00:19:44,440
Mr. Song

451
00:19:44,960 --> 00:19:46,510
is indeed full of talent!

452
00:19:46,720 --> 00:19:49,400
Now, Mr. Song, please present
the next challenge.

453
00:19:51,030 --> 00:19:52,440
Today, fine wines are gathered together.

454
00:19:52,590 --> 00:19:54,920
Let us dispel our worries in drink!

455
00:19:55,590 --> 00:19:56,790
Please listen to the next couplet:

456
00:19:57,240 --> 00:19:58,400
Within a pot, the world concealed;

457
00:19:58,830 --> 00:20:00,110
With skill and ease,
the blade moves free.

458
00:20:00,640 --> 00:20:02,440
Laugh, as butchers find their peace
in quiet retreat.

459
00:20:03,000 --> 00:20:04,350
- Great!
- Excellent!

460
00:20:04,350 --> 00:20:06,250
What a brilliant line!

461
00:20:06,270 --> 00:20:08,480
We've long heard of
Mr. Song's extraordinary talents;

462
00:20:08,480 --> 00:20:09,680
today we finally see it for ourselves.

463
00:20:09,790 --> 00:20:11,110
Truly deserving of his reputation.

464
00:20:11,480 --> 00:20:13,160
He has both family background
and talent.

465
00:20:13,350 --> 00:20:14,350
It seems Mr. Song will surely

466
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:17,030
come out on top in the spring exam.

467
00:20:17,160 --> 00:20:18,160
Indeed.

468
00:20:26,000 --> 00:20:27,160
Is there anyone

469
00:20:27,440 --> 00:20:29,310
who can match Mr. Song's couplet?

470
00:20:31,440 --> 00:20:33,480
Brother, why don't you step up?

471
00:20:33,880 --> 00:20:35,590
Are you afraid to lose to Mr. Song?

472
00:20:36,030 --> 00:20:36,880
Of course not.

473
00:20:37,830 --> 00:20:39,000
It's just a matter of hollow fame.

474
00:20:39,440 --> 00:20:40,480
Even if it's hollow fame,

475
00:20:41,200 --> 00:20:42,880
I still wish for you to fight for it.

476
00:20:43,640 --> 00:20:45,350
Here are nothing but
sons of noble houses.

477
00:20:45,880 --> 00:20:47,160
I want you to stand out,

478
00:20:47,400 --> 00:20:49,030
to inspire scholars from humble origins.

479
00:20:49,790 --> 00:20:51,110
Even if you don't take first place,

480
00:20:51,240 --> 00:20:52,790
you will surely surpass
most of them here.

481
00:20:55,270 --> 00:20:56,160
You're right.

482
00:20:58,030 --> 00:20:59,680
Then I shall represent
the sons of humble families

483
00:21:01,720 --> 00:21:03,070
and compete against

484
00:21:03,960 --> 00:21:04,800
the noble sons.

485
00:21:10,400 --> 00:21:11,350
I am willing to try.

486
00:21:12,270 --> 00:21:13,160
Mr. Lu, please.

487
00:21:13,160 --> 00:21:14,110
Who is this person?

488
00:21:14,110 --> 00:21:15,000
Mr. Lu?

489
00:21:15,880 --> 00:21:18,070
This Mr. Lu is unheard of.

490
00:21:18,240 --> 00:21:19,200
He must be of humble birth.

491
00:21:19,590 --> 00:21:21,270
Daring to challenge Mr. Song,

492
00:21:21,270 --> 00:21:23,200
how audacious.

493
00:21:23,440 --> 00:21:25,880
If he fails, it'll be embarrassing.

494
00:21:26,070 --> 00:21:26,910
Everyone, this is Lu Chang,

495
00:21:27,440 --> 00:21:29,070
the Prefectural Graduate of Jianglin,

496
00:21:29,790 --> 00:21:31,110
and my close friend.

497
00:21:34,200 --> 00:21:35,510
The sun and moon abide through time;

498
00:21:36,000 --> 00:21:37,480
Come, lift a cup and share our dreams.

499
00:21:37,790 --> 00:21:39,920
Ask not who shall claim the crown.

500
00:21:40,510 --> 00:21:41,790
- Nice lines!
- What a great match!

501
00:21:42,510 --> 00:21:43,440
Really good.

502
00:21:45,000 --> 00:21:46,070
Well said, Brother!

503
00:21:49,720 --> 00:21:51,920
Mr. Lu's brilliance shines through,

504
00:21:52,070 --> 00:21:53,160
rising from behind.

505
00:21:54,270 --> 00:21:56,680
Mr. Lu, please present
the next challenge.

506
00:21:57,110 --> 00:21:58,070
By a small lattice window,

507
00:21:58,590 --> 00:21:59,720
the song ends, guests drunk;

508
00:22:00,070 --> 00:22:02,680
A clear breeze joins the seats,
the bright moon leans on the eaves.

509
00:22:03,000 --> 00:22:05,270
A year's fine scenes—pray you remember;

510
00:22:06,070 --> 00:22:07,550
Ancient scents, ancient sights,
ancient names,

511
00:22:07,720 --> 00:22:08,750
all fulfill the olden dreams.

512
00:22:09,200 --> 00:22:11,550
Wearing green bamboo hats,
amid rushing rain and flying clouds;

513
00:22:11,550 --> 00:22:12,750
With emerald eaves for halls,

514
00:22:12,750 --> 00:22:13,790
and jade towers set for feasts.

515
00:22:13,880 --> 00:22:15,510
Speaking of times old and new,
I return again;

516
00:22:16,200 --> 00:22:17,880
Drunk on wind, drunk on moon,
drunk on wine—

517
00:22:18,240 --> 00:22:19,310
yet better still, drunk at heart.

518
00:22:20,070 --> 00:22:21,160
- Well done!
- Bravo!

519
00:22:24,270 --> 00:22:25,880
What a thrill!

520
00:22:26,200 --> 00:22:28,750
Mr. Lu, please continue
to present the challenge.

521
00:22:31,510 --> 00:22:32,350
Mr. Song,

522
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:34,840
listen carefully.

523
00:22:36,480 --> 00:22:37,440
A gathering to judge the wine,

524
00:22:37,880 --> 00:22:38,820
a gathering to savor its soul;

525
00:22:39,270 --> 00:22:41,110
At the judging, savor the soul of wine;

526
00:22:42,070 --> 00:22:43,170
The gathering lives through ages,

527
00:22:43,640 --> 00:22:45,400
the spirit of wine endures through time.

528
00:22:52,000 --> 00:22:53,880
This upper line sounds simple,

529
00:22:54,070 --> 00:22:55,160
but if you savor it carefully,

530
00:22:55,480 --> 00:22:58,790
you'll find profound depth within.

531
00:22:59,000 --> 00:23:00,720
- Yes.
- Indeed.

532
00:23:05,440 --> 00:23:06,280
Everyone,

533
00:23:06,590 --> 00:23:09,590
is there anyone who can match
Mr. Lu's couplet?

534
00:23:09,880 --> 00:23:10,960
If not,

535
00:23:11,070 --> 00:23:13,400
then Mr. Lu shall be the winner.

536
00:23:13,720 --> 00:23:15,270
Even Mr. Song couldn't match it?

537
00:23:15,640 --> 00:23:17,440
Even Mr. Song couldn't match it?

538
00:23:19,720 --> 00:23:20,880
Mr. Lu's upper line

539
00:23:21,640 --> 00:23:22,720
balances movement and stillness,

540
00:23:22,880 --> 00:23:23,830
truly a masterpiece.

541
00:23:24,480 --> 00:23:26,960
The words are familiar yet fresh,
and they fit the occasion.

542
00:23:29,070 --> 00:23:31,200
I am dull-witted and unable to answer.

543
00:23:44,960 --> 00:23:47,510
"the spirit of wine
endures through time." Nice!

544
00:23:48,070 --> 00:23:48,920
I hereby announce,

545
00:23:49,590 --> 00:23:53,030
today's winner is Mr. Lu!

546
00:23:53,030 --> 00:23:55,240
- Good job!
- Congrats!

547
00:23:57,510 --> 00:23:58,400
Mr. Lu.

548
00:23:58,750 --> 00:23:59,850
- Please.
- Congratulations, Mr. Lu.

549
00:24:03,900 --> 00:24:04,760
Everyone,

550
00:24:04,880 --> 00:24:07,200
this golden goblet now
belongs to Mr. Lu.

551
00:24:08,270 --> 00:24:10,030
Congratulations, Mr. Lu!

552
00:24:10,750 --> 00:24:11,590
Thank you.

553
00:24:12,590 --> 00:24:13,720
Mr. Lu,

554
00:24:13,920 --> 00:24:15,270
which tavern's wine has caught your eye?

555
00:24:15,400 --> 00:24:17,350
Please compose a poem for it.

556
00:24:29,200 --> 00:24:30,110
I choose that one.

557
00:24:32,040 --> 00:24:33,300
Why did he choose their wine?

558
00:24:33,750 --> 00:24:35,590
(Lanzhi Wine, Drunken River Tower)
Grandpa, Mr. Lu has won!

559
00:24:36,240 --> 00:24:37,440
He has won!

560
00:24:40,540 --> 00:24:42,220
(Pine pollen)

561
00:24:45,540 --> 00:24:47,220
(Tea)

562
00:24:48,030 --> 00:24:51,680
Pine pollen infused in wine,
spring water brewed for tea,

563
00:24:52,030 --> 00:24:56,110
sober beneath the bright moon,
drunk amidst the clear breeze.

564
00:24:56,830 --> 00:25:00,000
What a poem!

565
00:25:00,000 --> 00:25:00,980
Good!

566
00:25:00,980 --> 00:25:02,660
(Lu Chang)

567
00:25:03,510 --> 00:25:06,790
Mr. Lu, may I ask the name of this wine?

568
00:25:07,790 --> 00:25:09,000
Drunken Pine Pollen.

569
00:25:10,790 --> 00:25:11,630
Excellent!

570
00:25:12,100 --> 00:25:12,950
Sir,

571
00:25:13,070 --> 00:25:15,550
our restaurant will purchase
all your wine.

572
00:25:15,790 --> 00:25:17,960
Later, we will settle the account
with you.

573
00:25:18,270 --> 00:25:20,590
If Mr. Lu becomes the top scholar,

574
00:25:20,590 --> 00:25:22,880
your wine will be crowned
the Top Scholar's Wine!

575
00:25:23,680 --> 00:25:25,000
Thank you, Mr. Lu!

576
00:25:25,400 --> 00:25:26,550
Thank you, Mr. Song!

577
00:25:27,680 --> 00:25:29,030
Today's victory Mr. Lu

578
00:25:29,480 --> 00:25:31,720
will surely inspire many scholars
from humble families

579
00:25:32,110 --> 00:25:33,400
to march forward bravely.

580
00:25:33,920 --> 00:25:35,510
I live among the common folk

581
00:25:35,830 --> 00:25:38,640
and know the power of word of mouth.

582
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:40,480
Thank you, sir.

583
00:25:46,680 --> 00:25:47,880
Do you mind

584
00:25:48,160 --> 00:25:49,270
not winning today?

585
00:25:49,920 --> 00:25:50,940
Exchanging couplets with Mr. Lu

586
00:25:51,030 --> 00:25:52,440
was a great joy of life.

587
00:25:53,240 --> 00:25:54,310
Seeing Mr. Lu display his talent,

588
00:25:54,310 --> 00:25:55,400
I am delighted.

589
00:25:55,830 --> 00:25:57,720
Thank you for thinking of my brother.

590
00:25:58,550 --> 00:25:59,550
To have a friend like you

591
00:25:59,880 --> 00:26:01,350
is truly a great blessing in life.

592
00:26:01,880 --> 00:26:04,070
Mingshu, you are too kind.

593
00:26:04,160 --> 00:26:06,030
Mr. Lu is also talented and virtuous,

594
00:26:06,030 --> 00:26:06,920
truly outstanding.

595
00:26:07,480 --> 00:26:09,480
Mr. Lu is indeed full of talent.

596
00:26:09,480 --> 00:26:11,720
Though of humble origins,
he is still worthy of marriage.

597
00:26:11,740 --> 00:26:12,600
Indeed.

598
00:26:12,610 --> 00:26:13,760
What do you mean "worthy of marriage"?

599
00:26:14,000 --> 00:26:15,750
He may not even fancy you lot!

600
00:26:16,720 --> 00:26:17,560
Let's go.

601
00:26:27,200 --> 00:26:28,040
This is for you.

602
00:26:31,590 --> 00:26:32,430
Thank you, Brother.

603
00:26:34,160 --> 00:26:35,240
Today, Mr. Lu has taken the stage

604
00:26:35,550 --> 00:26:37,070
and secured his place
among the noble ladies.

605
00:26:41,750 --> 00:26:42,590
Lady Mingshu,

606
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:44,030
please come with me.

607
00:26:53,000 --> 00:26:54,310
Though I didn't win today,

608
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:56,880
a tavern gifted me a bottle of
Rose Dew Wine.

609
00:26:57,440 --> 00:26:58,310
This wine is mild,

610
00:26:58,880 --> 00:26:59,830
perfect for you.

611
00:27:03,880 --> 00:27:05,200
Early spring is still cold,

612
00:27:05,510 --> 00:27:06,880
it's easy to catch a chill.

613
00:27:07,480 --> 00:27:08,750
Be careful not to fall ill.

614
00:27:13,240 --> 00:27:16,270
(Though Xie Xi's actions are intimate,)

615
00:27:16,640 --> 00:27:18,920
(his manner remains proper
and gracious.)

616
00:27:19,920 --> 00:27:21,240
Earlier, when you were on stage,

617
00:27:21,240 --> 00:27:22,080
you had no idea

618
00:27:22,240 --> 00:27:23,680
how the young ladies in the crowd

619
00:27:23,830 --> 00:27:25,240
were looking at you.

620
00:27:26,750 --> 00:27:28,480
Since you and I are already engaged,

621
00:27:28,640 --> 00:27:30,880
no other woman will ever catch my eye.

622
00:27:31,840 --> 00:27:32,710
However,

623
00:27:32,830 --> 00:27:34,720
today's gathering is quite rowdy.

624
00:27:35,000 --> 00:27:36,750
I fear someone may get drunk

625
00:27:36,750 --> 00:27:37,720
and offend you.

626
00:27:38,000 --> 00:27:38,840
So,

627
00:27:39,160 --> 00:27:40,400
how about I escort you home early?

628
00:27:40,920 --> 00:27:41,760
My Lady,

629
00:27:42,480 --> 00:27:44,200
Mr. Xie's friends are outside asking

630
00:27:44,200 --> 00:27:47,310
for him to come down to drink
and compose poetry.

631
00:27:48,070 --> 00:27:49,680
Tell them to wait. Tell them

632
00:27:49,920 --> 00:27:51,090
I'm attending to the County Princess.

633
00:27:52,070 --> 00:27:53,250
Since we rarely get to see each other,

634
00:27:53,590 --> 00:27:54,640
I wish to spend time with you.

635
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:58,480
Don't make them wait too long.

636
00:27:58,480 --> 00:27:59,440
Go entertain them.

637
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:00,880
My carriage is right outside,

638
00:28:00,880 --> 00:28:02,000
ready to leave at any time.

639
00:28:02,510 --> 00:28:03,350
Very well.

640
00:28:03,350 --> 00:28:05,480
Then I'll be downstairs.

641
00:28:05,640 --> 00:28:07,400
If anything happens, just call for me.

642
00:28:36,880 --> 00:28:39,310
Xie Xi is gentle and elegant,

643
00:28:39,720 --> 00:28:41,590
and shows deep affection toward you,

644
00:28:42,200 --> 00:28:43,640
unlike someone whose heart has changed.

645
00:28:44,400 --> 00:28:45,240
He seems

646
00:28:45,240 --> 00:28:47,240
like a flawless lover.

647
00:28:48,790 --> 00:28:50,750
But there is no such thing
as true perfection!

648
00:28:51,400 --> 00:28:52,400
Either such flaws

649
00:28:52,400 --> 00:28:53,550
have yet to be discovered by others,

650
00:28:54,200 --> 00:28:55,040
or

651
00:28:57,350 --> 00:28:59,880
the perfection itself
is but an illusion.

652
00:29:01,030 --> 00:29:02,350
I understand what you mean.

653
00:29:03,480 --> 00:29:06,240
Everyone harbors selfishness
and emotions.

654
00:29:06,830 --> 00:29:07,830
But Mr. Xie

655
00:29:07,830 --> 00:29:09,720
acts too flawlessly,

656
00:29:10,880 --> 00:29:14,070
his emotions too rational,

657
00:29:14,070 --> 00:29:15,160
not like true affection.

658
00:29:15,480 --> 00:29:16,320
Exactly.

659
00:29:16,550 --> 00:29:17,390
That's it.

660
00:29:17,880 --> 00:29:19,790
Though he appears attentive toward me,

661
00:29:20,400 --> 00:29:22,720
there's an indescribable
sense of calculation.

662
00:29:23,160 --> 00:29:24,510
As if it were all premeditated.

663
00:29:25,510 --> 00:29:27,400
I can't quite point out what's wrong,

664
00:29:27,400 --> 00:29:28,680
but I just feel that something is off.

665
00:29:32,480 --> 00:29:34,880
For instance, when he put clothes
on you—

666
00:29:35,110 --> 00:29:37,680
this room clearly had a brazier burning.

667
00:29:37,960 --> 00:29:41,000
Even in early spring,
it wasn't that cold.

668
00:29:41,720 --> 00:29:44,440
It looked like concern,

669
00:29:44,440 --> 00:29:45,720
but in truth,

670
00:29:45,720 --> 00:29:47,680
it was a rehearsed move,

671
00:29:48,000 --> 00:29:49,070
not heartfelt.

672
00:29:49,590 --> 00:29:50,430
Yes.

673
00:29:50,640 --> 00:29:51,480
Exactly like that.

674
00:29:52,480 --> 00:29:54,310
But I've investigated him
for over half a year,

675
00:29:54,720 --> 00:29:55,560
and I—

676
00:29:55,830 --> 00:29:57,350
I've found nothing suspicious.

677
00:29:57,590 --> 00:29:59,110
It leaves me at a complete loss.

678
00:30:02,920 --> 00:30:04,550
He usually stays at the academy.

679
00:30:05,070 --> 00:30:06,030
Have you checked the academy?

680
00:30:06,680 --> 00:30:07,520
The academy?

681
00:30:08,550 --> 00:30:09,750
What is there to investigate there?

682
00:30:09,750 --> 00:30:10,720
It's full of men.

683
00:30:11,550 --> 00:30:13,070
(It's all men...)

684
00:30:13,880 --> 00:30:15,240
(How would I go about investigating?)

685
00:30:16,260 --> 00:30:17,640
(Jinzun Restaurant)

686
00:30:17,640 --> 00:30:18,480
Shishu.

687
00:30:19,640 --> 00:30:20,480
Let me help.

688
00:30:21,480 --> 00:30:23,070
How much did he drink?

689
00:30:23,070 --> 00:30:24,200
How did he get so drunk?

690
00:30:24,550 --> 00:30:25,720
Someone pulled him into a few rounds.

691
00:30:25,960 --> 00:30:27,680
He drank too fast and couldn't hold it.

692
00:30:27,880 --> 00:30:29,720
Mr. Lu, the gathering's over.

693
00:30:29,880 --> 00:30:31,200
Let's head back to the academy.

694
00:30:32,480 --> 00:30:34,000
This wine's not bad.

695
00:30:35,640 --> 00:30:36,550
Where's Mingshu?

696
00:30:37,700 --> 00:30:38,550
Mingshu...

697
00:30:38,640 --> 00:30:40,240
Even drunk, he's thinking about Mingshu.

698
00:30:40,480 --> 00:30:41,340
Let's go home.

699
00:30:41,340 --> 00:30:43,030
Consort Rui sent a carriage for Mingshu.

700
00:30:43,400 --> 00:30:44,240
Here, here,

701
00:30:45,960 --> 00:30:46,800
easy.

702
00:31:00,440 --> 00:31:01,280
Mr. Lu,

703
00:31:08,000 --> 00:31:08,840
careful.

704
00:31:14,140 --> 00:31:18,380
(Heaven Rewards Diligence)

705
00:31:24,640 --> 00:31:25,480
Mr. Lu...

706
00:31:27,160 --> 00:31:28,070
Does Mingshu

707
00:31:29,720 --> 00:31:31,200
have any affection for me?

708
00:31:33,350 --> 00:31:34,200
Mingshu...

709
00:31:35,110 --> 00:31:35,950
Mingshu...

710
00:31:39,790 --> 00:31:40,630
Mingshu...

711
00:31:42,590 --> 00:31:44,030
Where's Mingshu?

712
00:31:44,400 --> 00:31:45,240
She's already gone home.

713
00:31:47,000 --> 00:31:47,840
Mingshu...

714
00:31:49,070 --> 00:31:49,910
Drink some water.

715
00:31:51,440 --> 00:31:52,280
Come on.

716
00:31:52,720 --> 00:31:53,560
Mr. Lu...

717
00:31:55,610 --> 00:31:56,520
Thank you.

718
00:31:56,640 --> 00:31:57,570
Here, here.

719
00:32:00,790 --> 00:32:01,630
Drink some water.

720
00:32:06,960 --> 00:32:07,800
Mr. Lu.

721
00:32:08,270 --> 00:32:09,110
Mr. Lu.

722
00:32:09,270 --> 00:32:10,110
Are you feeling unwell?

723
00:32:11,550 --> 00:32:12,390
It's mine.

724
00:32:13,110 --> 00:32:13,950
It's yours?

725
00:32:14,510 --> 00:32:15,350
It's mine.

726
00:32:16,070 --> 00:32:16,910
What is yours?

727
00:32:17,240 --> 00:32:18,110
It's mine.

728
00:32:18,480 --> 00:32:19,320
Mr. Lu!

729
00:32:19,440 --> 00:32:20,280
Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu!

730
00:32:21,830 --> 00:32:22,670
Mr. Lu!

731
00:32:31,550 --> 00:32:32,510
- It's mine.
- Mr. Lu.

732
00:32:38,070 --> 00:32:38,910
It's mine.

733
00:32:46,400 --> 00:32:47,510
Who would've thought

734
00:32:48,550 --> 00:32:50,280
the scholarly, upright top scorer,

735
00:32:51,480 --> 00:32:52,960
after a few drinks,
would be so troublesome?

736
00:32:58,440 --> 00:33:01,480
Sometimes, the most dangerous place
is the safest.

737
00:33:02,680 --> 00:33:04,350
What seems least likely

738
00:33:04,480 --> 00:33:06,160
is often the hardest to detect.

739
00:33:07,790 --> 00:33:10,550
The clue might just be
in Songling Academy.

740
00:33:11,200 --> 00:33:12,070
What do you think?

741
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:15,110
However,

742
00:33:15,240 --> 00:33:17,440
there's a difficulty for me.

743
00:33:18,160 --> 00:33:19,400
If I go to the academy,

744
00:33:19,830 --> 00:33:21,920
I'll have to live in the same place
as my brother.

745
00:33:24,750 --> 00:33:25,770
That absolutely cannot happen!

746
00:33:27,640 --> 00:33:28,920
You feel the same way, don't you?

747
00:33:34,550 --> 00:33:35,390
What?

748
00:33:35,680 --> 00:33:36,520
You...

749
00:33:36,790 --> 00:33:38,350
You want to become his page?

750
00:33:39,420 --> 00:33:41,200
But a page has to do chores!

751
00:33:41,200 --> 00:33:42,240
You won't be able to handle it.

752
00:33:42,720 --> 00:33:45,110
Those things won't be a problem for me.

753
00:33:45,310 --> 00:33:46,350
I'll learn as I go.

754
00:33:47,640 --> 00:33:49,480
But... does Mr. Lu know

755
00:33:49,880 --> 00:33:51,160
about you entering the academy?

756
00:33:54,720 --> 00:33:56,110
I know your purpose
for going to the academy.

757
00:33:56,510 --> 00:33:57,960
But from what I know of Xie Xi,

758
00:33:58,160 --> 00:33:59,590
he doesn't seem to be unfaithful.

759
00:34:00,000 --> 00:34:01,630
He shows no unusual behavior
at the academy either.

760
00:34:02,110 --> 00:34:03,240
Perhaps you should give up?

761
00:34:04,240 --> 00:34:06,440
Xie Xi's conduct and demeanor

762
00:34:06,590 --> 00:34:07,830
are too flawless.

763
00:34:08,150 --> 00:34:09,590
But there's no such thing
as a perfect man.

764
00:34:10,150 --> 00:34:12,190
I suspect Xie Xi
must be hiding something.

765
00:34:13,070 --> 00:34:14,800
Since he's living at the academy,

766
00:34:14,960 --> 00:34:17,070
the flaw must be hidden there.

767
00:34:17,590 --> 00:34:18,630
I must go to the academy,

768
00:34:18,630 --> 00:34:20,110
observe him up close,

769
00:34:20,590 --> 00:34:21,840
and get to the bottom of this.

770
00:34:22,920 --> 00:34:24,630
I know what you're concerned about.

771
00:34:24,880 --> 00:34:25,760
I absolutely won't

772
00:34:26,360 --> 00:34:27,550
cause you any trouble.

773
00:34:29,030 --> 00:34:31,030
Aren't you worried that
I might tell Mr. Lu?

774
00:34:31,630 --> 00:34:32,480
I trust you.

775
00:34:36,800 --> 00:34:37,640
But...

776
00:34:39,280 --> 00:34:40,120
Have some water.

777
00:34:43,840 --> 00:34:44,680
Alright.

778
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:46,240
Wait, no,

779
00:34:47,000 --> 00:34:47,840
then where should I go?

780
00:34:50,670 --> 00:34:51,710
You don't look very well.

781
00:34:52,360 --> 00:34:53,360
Go back and rest for a few days.

782
00:34:54,030 --> 00:34:54,870
I...

783
00:35:06,420 --> 00:35:10,260
(Songling Academy)

784
00:35:10,260 --> 00:35:12,860
(Mingli Hall)

785
00:35:22,480 --> 00:35:23,630
- Mr. Song.
- Mr. Song.

786
00:35:39,110 --> 00:35:40,150
This is your room?

787
00:35:41,320 --> 00:35:42,160
Take a look.

788
00:35:45,240 --> 00:35:46,840
Mingshu, since you're a girl,

789
00:35:46,960 --> 00:35:48,320
you should stay in the inner room.

790
00:35:48,550 --> 00:35:49,630
I'll study in the outer room.

791
00:35:55,190 --> 00:35:56,760
You've already helped me a lot;

792
00:35:56,960 --> 00:35:58,230
how could I trouble you further?

793
00:35:58,550 --> 00:36:00,190
I'm just happy you're here;

794
00:36:00,360 --> 00:36:01,200
there's no talk of trouble.

795
00:36:01,840 --> 00:36:02,920
I've thought it through,

796
00:36:03,030 --> 00:36:03,880
since I'm new here,

797
00:36:03,880 --> 00:36:05,070
I need to quickly get familiar

798
00:36:05,070 --> 00:36:06,190
with Xie Xi's daily routines.

799
00:36:06,250 --> 00:36:07,690
That way, it'll be easier
for me to investigate.

800
00:36:11,320 --> 00:36:13,190
Life at the academy is quite orderly.

801
00:36:13,880 --> 00:36:15,550
The students rise at Mao hour

802
00:36:15,840 --> 00:36:16,960
and recite texts for an hour.

803
00:36:18,740 --> 00:36:20,290
Breakfast is at the third quarter
of the Mao hour.

804
00:36:20,760 --> 00:36:22,030
Classes start at the Chen hour

805
00:36:22,030 --> 00:36:22,960
and end by noon.

806
00:36:23,360 --> 00:36:24,710
After that, students

807
00:36:24,710 --> 00:36:26,480
do their assignments or self-study.

808
00:36:27,400 --> 00:36:29,280
Some return to their rooms;
some go to the library.

809
00:36:30,320 --> 00:36:31,960
I won't be able to enter Xie Xi's room,

810
00:36:32,590 --> 00:36:35,110
so I'll observe him in class
and at the library.

811
00:36:36,320 --> 00:36:37,360
Don't rush.

812
00:36:37,550 --> 00:36:38,400
You've just arrived.

813
00:36:38,400 --> 00:36:39,440
Get familiar with here first.

814
00:36:39,670 --> 00:36:40,660
Come, let me show you something.

815
00:36:43,000 --> 00:36:43,840
What is it?

816
00:36:46,670 --> 00:36:47,510
Please sit.

817
00:36:49,550 --> 00:36:50,550
What is it?

818
00:36:54,740 --> 00:36:56,900
(Ladies' Jewelry Illustrations)
Look.

819
00:37:00,690 --> 00:37:02,420
(Malachite Blossom Inlaid Hairpiece)
I was afraid you'd be bored,

820
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:03,690
(Red Agate Phoenix Headpiece)
so I brought this

821
00:37:03,700 --> 00:37:04,760
from the study at home.

822
00:37:05,190 --> 00:37:07,030
I thought it might inspire you
in designing jewelry.

823
00:37:07,360 --> 00:37:09,320
The illustrations are so beautiful.

824
00:37:09,800 --> 00:37:11,800
This book is truly a rare find.

825
00:37:13,000 --> 00:37:13,840
I'm glad you like it.

826
00:37:15,440 --> 00:37:16,280
Qingzhao,

827
00:37:16,670 --> 00:37:17,590
you really are the gentlest

828
00:37:17,590 --> 00:37:19,070
and most thoughtful man in this world.

829
00:37:26,040 --> 00:37:26,880
There's a style

830
00:37:26,880 --> 00:37:28,110
you've never seen before.

831
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:29,440
You'll surely be interested.

832
00:37:31,940 --> 00:37:33,940
(Cloud-Cutting Snow-Touched
with Cinnabar)

833
00:37:37,780 --> 00:37:40,910
♪Two swallows dart
through the drizzle♪

